{"tid":1474132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"論外交部對中國主權所謂的合理性","createTime":"2019-08-15T05:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T05:22:05.000Z","uid":86498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"58a8016410035a09a8e35315c70a075e13eb8e43","tid":1474132,"uid":86498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"不如用歷史討論一下<br />\n<br />\n1) 1689年俄羅斯與滿清政府簽《尼布楚條約》中訂明海參崴屬於清朝，1858年《璦琿條約》逼清政府將包括海參崴的烏蘇里江以東地區為清俄共管。1860年《清俄北京條約》逼清政府割讓烏蘇里江以東包括庫頁島在內的40萬平方千米的領土。<br />\n<br />\n2) 1842年《中英南京條約》清朝永久割讓香港島連同鄰近鴨脷洲予英國。1860年永久割讓九龍半島南部連同鄰近昂船洲一帶予英國。1898年《展拓香港界址專條》租借九龍半島北部、新界和鄰近兩百多個島嶼99年。<br />\n<br />\n既然中國外交部多次宣稱「任何時候，中國主權和領土的完整神聖不可侵犯」<br />\n那麼香港跟海參崴一樣在滿清時期被不平等條約被割讓既土地.<br />\n為何今天中國只在那邊維護香港的領土完整，海參崴呢？<br />\n<br />\n1917年蘇聯自願放棄其在中國的特權，但在領土上未完全兌現，亦無退還條約中獲得的領土，且歷屆蘇聯、俄羅斯政府均否認這些條約是「不平等條約」。<br />\n<br />\n最重要的是俄羅斯直到今日侵占了約160萬平方公里的土地（不包括外蒙），而這些土地，是蘇聯領導人列寧曾經3次發表政府聲明要歸還給中國的。<br />\n<br />\n那請問認為「任何時候，中國主權和領土的完整神聖不可侵犯」的中國政府，為什麼不兌現這在歷史上被俄羅斯侵占的160萬平方公里土地呢?"},{"pid":"efd27ab22b9ff03011f0685980cd05a96628d5f4","tid":1474132,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67661830c55d23622b44105e7a71cf60fc8ade02","tid":1474132,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b506b07785e9f80a0e0b60c38d3ab6e627b23d3b","tid":1474132,"uid":284804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"因為成個中國都係俄羅斯不可分割嘅一部份 唯一合理解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}